Dialogue: 0,01:56:40.28,01:56:41.28,Default,,0,0,0,,这里有什么东西	What do we got here?
Dialogue: 0,01:56:41.28,01:56:42.28,Default,,0,0,0,,有空速	We've got airspeed.
Dialogue: 0,01:56:43.28,01:56:44.28,Default,,0,0,0,,空速	Airspeed.
Dialogue: 0,01:56:45.28,01:56:47.28,Default,,0,0,0,,好 动力 这是动力	Okay, power. This is power.
Dialogue: 0,01:56:53.28,01:56:56.28,Default,,0,0,0,,有效载荷 我如何卸掉这个有效载荷	Payload. How do I get rid of this payload?
