Dialogue: 0,01:58:47.28,01:58:48.28,Default,,0,0,0,,太过了	Whoa, whoa, too much. Too much.
Dialogue: 0,01:58:49.28,01:58:50.28,Default,,0,0,0,,该死 	Oh, shit!
Dialogue: 0,01:58:51.28,01:58:53.28,Default,,0,0,0,,往上拉升	Pull up. Pull up.
