Dialogue: 0,01:58:59.28,01:59:01.28,Default,,0,0,0,,接近地面	Terrain. Terrain.
Dialogue: 0,01:59:19.28,01:59:20.28,Default,,0,0,0,,班吉 我什么都找不到	Benji, I'm not finding anything.
Dialogue: 0,01:59:21.28,01:59:22.28,Default,,0,0,0,,我觉得我们找错地方了	I think we're looking in the wrong place.
Dialogue: 0,01:59:23.28,01:59:24.28,Default,,0,0,0,,到处都有信号	Signatures everywhere.
Dialogue: 0,01:59:24.28,01:59:25.28,Default,,0,0,0,,这是藏炸弹的绝佳地方	This is the perfect place to hide it.
Dialogue: 0,01:59:25.28,01:59:28.28,Default,,0,0,0,,我就是这个意思 我了解连恩 如果我们在这里找	That's the point. I know Lane. If we're looking here,
