Dialogue: 0,01:59:34.28,01:59:35.28,Default,,0,0,0,,我去村子那里	I'm heading to the village.
Dialogue: 0,01:59:35.28,01:59:37.28,Default,,0,0,0,,等等我 好吗	Just wait for me, all right?
