Dialogue: 0,01:59:46.28,01:59:49.28,Default,,0,0,0,,剪断这里这根电线	Cut this wire right here.
Dialogue: 0,01:59:50.28,01:59:54.28,Default,,0,0,0,,朝逆时针方向慢慢旋转那个螺丝钉	Turn that screw counterclockwise, very slowly.
