Dialogue: 0,01:59:57.28,01:59:58.28,Default,,0,0,0,,那么	So...
Dialogue: 0,02:00:00.28,02:00:01.28,Default,,0,0,0,,他还好吗	How is he?
Dialogue: 0,02:00:01.28,02:00:04.28,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道的 伊森还是老样子	Oh, you know. Same old Ethan.
