Dialogue: 0,02:00:18.28,02:00:20.28,Default,,0,0,0,,该死 	Oh, shit!
Dialogue: 0,02:00:20.28,02:00:22.28,Default,,0,0,0,,不要	No, no, no, no, no, no.
Dialogue: 0,02:00:30.28,02:00:33.28,Default,,0,0,0,,-班吉 我看见连恩了 -什么在哪里	-Benji, I see Lane. -What? Where?
Dialogue: 0,02:00:33.28,02:00:34.28,Default,,0,0,0,,他在村子边缘的一栋房子里	He's in a house at the edge of the village.
Dialogue: 0,02:00:34.28,02:00:36.28,Default,,0,0,0,,好 等等我 好吗	All right, just wait for me, okay?
Dialogue: 0,02:00:37.28,02:00:38.28,Default,,0,0,0,,艾尔莎 等等我 	Ilsa, wait for me!
Dialogue: 0,02:00:48.28,02:00:49.28,Default,,0,0,0,,不	No.
