Dialogue: 0,02:07:37.28,02:07:38.28,Default,,0,0,0,,把他绑起来	Tie him up.
Dialogue: 0,02:08:42.28,02:08:44.28,Default,,0,0,0,,你为何就是死不了	Why won't you just die?
