Dialogue: 0,02:13:13.28,02:13:15.28,Default,,0,0,0,,拿开那个主板 你会看到	Remove that panel and you'll see
Dialogue: 0,02:13:15.28,02:13:17.28,Default,,0,0,0,,保险丝的电源和接地电线	the power and ground wires for the fuse.
Dialogue: 0,02:13:17.28,02:13:18.28,Default,,0,0,0,,看到了	Got it.
Dialogue: 0,02:13:18.28,02:13:20.28,Default,,0,0,0,,到那个时候 剪断绿色电线	When the time comes, cut the green wire.
Dialogue: 0,02:13:20.28,02:13:22.28,Default,,0,0,0,,现在不要剪	Do not cut it yet.
