Dialogue: 0,02:13:55.28,02:13:56.28,Default,,0,0,0,,我们能决定吗	Can we make a decision on this?
Dialogue: 0,02:13:56.28,02:13:58.28,Default,,0,0,0,,好 我们还剩一秒钟时剪	All right, all right! We'll do it on one.
Dialogue: 0,02:13:58.28,02:13:58.28,Default,,0,0,0,,还剩一秒钟时剪	Cutting on one?
Dialogue: 0,02:13:58.28,02:14:00.28,Default,,0,0,0,,对 一秒 好 准备	Yes, one. All right, stand by.
