Dialogue: 0,02:16:12.28,02:16:13.28,Default,,0,0,0,,你可真幸运	You're a lucky man.
Dialogue: 0,02:16:14.28,02:16:16.28,Default,,0,0,0,,你坠机后得以生还 真是奇迹 索恩医生	It's a miracle that crash didn't kill you, Dr. Thorne.
Dialogue: 0,02:16:17.28,02:16:18.28,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你的朋友没在一小时后找到你	If your friend didn't find you an hour later,
Dialogue: 0,02:16:18.28,02:16:20.28,Default,,0,0,0,,你会死于冻伤	you would've died of exposure.
Dialogue: 0,02:16:20.28,02:16:22.28,Default,,0,0,0,,-我的朋友 -是的	-My friends? -Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,02:16:24.28,02:16:26.28,Default,,0,0,0,,你才刚离开 她就来了	She got here not long after you left.
Dialogue: 0,02:16:27.28,02:16:29.28,Default,,0,0,0,,还带来了很多印度士兵	Right in front of half the Indian Army.
Dialogue: 0,02:16:30.28,02:16:32.28,Default,,0,0,0,,能让我们单独谈谈吗	Can you give us a few minutes, please?
Dialogue: 0,02:16:35.28,02:16:36.28,Default,,0,0,0,,回头见 医生	See you later, Doc.
Dialogue: 0,02:16:43.28,02:16:44.28,Default,,0,0,0,,朱莉娅	Julia...
Dialogue: 0,02:16:46.28,02:16:47.28,Default,,0,0,0,,对不起	I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,02:16:48.28,02:16:49.28,Default,,0,0,0,,根本用不着道歉	There's no reason to be sorry.
Dialogue: 0,02:16:49.28,02:16:50.28,Default,,0,0,0,,不是的	No.
Dialogue: 0,02:16:51.28,02:16:52.28,Default,,0,0,0,,对于发生的一切	I'm sorry
Dialogue: 0,02:16:54.28,02:16:56.28,Default,,0,0,0,,我都很抱歉 我	for everything. I...
Dialogue: 0,02:16:57.28,02:16:58.28,Default,,0,0,0,,看着我	Look at me.
Dialogue: 0,02:16:59.28,02:17:01.28,Default,,0,0,0,,看着我	Look at me.
Dialogue: 0,02:17:01.28,02:17:03.28,Default,,0,0,0,,看看我的人生	Look at my life.
Dialogue: 0,02:17:05.28,02:17:08.28,Default,,0,0,0,,我热爱自己的事业 如果我没遇到你	I love what I do, and I never would have
Dialogue: 0,02:17:08.28,02:17:10.28,Default,,0,0,0,,就不会找到这一切	found this if I hadn't met you.
Dialogue: 0,02:17:11.28,02:17:13.28,Default,,0,0,0,,发生的一切	And everything that happened,
Dialogue: 0,02:17:14.28,02:17:17.28,Default,,0,0,0,,让我了解真实的自己 让我明白	it taught me who I am. It showed me
Dialogue: 0,02:17:17.28,02:17:20.28,Default,,0,0,0,,自己的能力 而且我	what I am capable of, and I...
Dialogue: 0,02:17:20.28,02:17:22.28,Default,,0,0,0,,我会活下去	I am a survivor.
Dialogue: 0,02:17:22.28,02:17:24.28,Default,,0,0,0,,但这里发生的一切	But what happened here,
Dialogue: 0,02:17:26.28,02:17:27.28,Default,,0,0,0,,-是我的 -平安无事	-it was my... -Nothing happened.
Dialogue: 0,02:17:28.28,02:17:29.28,Default,,0,0,0,,因为你守候着我	Because you were here.
Dialogue: 0,02:17:32.28,02:17:35.28,Default,,0,0,0,,知道你永远都会与我相守 我便能每夜安眠	And I sleep soundly at night knowing you always will be.
Dialogue: 0,02:17:44.28,02:17:46.28,Default,,0,0,0,,你幸福吗	You're happy?
Dialogue: 0,02:17:46.28,02:17:47.28,Default,,0,0,0,,非常幸福	Very.
Dialogue: 0,02:17:50.28,02:17:52.28,Default,,0,0,0,,我身处自己的归属地	I'm exactly where I should be.
Dialogue: 0,02:17:55.28,02:17:56.28,Default,,0,0,0,,你也一样	And so are you.
Dialogue: 0,02:18:36.28,02:18:37.28,Default,,0,0,0,,根据你的要求	Per your request,
Dialogue: 0,02:18:39.28,02:18:43.28,Default,,0,0,0,,我会把所罗门连恩交给军情六处	I'm handing Solomon Lane back to MI6.
Dialogue: 0,02:18:47.28,02:18:49.28,Default,,0,0,0,,当然是通过中间人	Through a broker, of course.
Dialogue: 0,02:18:51.28,02:18:54.28,Default,,0,0,0,,这是日前安排的一部分	Part of our ongoing arrangement.
Dialogue: 0,02:18:59.28,02:19:01.28,Default,,0,0,0,,巴黎事件之后	After what happened in Paris,
Dialogue: 0,02:19:02.28,02:19:05.28,Default,,0,0,0,,我们更倾向于保持低调	we prefer to keep a low profile.
Dialogue: 0,02:19:07.28,02:19:11.28,Default,,0,0,0,,你的朋友无需 再跟英国秘密情报局打交道了	And that closes your friend's account with British Intelligence.
Dialogue: 0,02:19:13.28,02:19:15.28,Default,,0,0,0,,肋骨 小心我的肋骨	The ribs. Watch the ribs.
Dialogue: 0,02:19:16.28,02:19:19.28,Default,,0,0,0,,我现在明白了汉利为何信任你	I understand now why Hunley believed in you.
Dialogue: 0,02:19:20.28,02:19:22.28,Default,,0,0,0,,世界需要不可能任务小组	The world needs the IMF.
Dialogue: 0,02:19:23.28,02:19:25.28,Default,,0,0,0,,我们需要像你这样的人	We need people like you
Dialogue: 0,02:19:26.28,02:19:27.28,Default,,0,0,0,,你在乎一个人的性命	who care about the one life
Dialogue: 0,02:19:28.28,02:19:31.28,Default,,0,0,0,,也在乎无数人的性命	as much as they care about the millions.
Dialogue: 0,02:19:33.28,02:19:34.28,Default,,0,0,0,,这样一来	That way
Dialogue: 0,02:19:34.28,02:19:36.28,Default,,0,0,0,,我就永远无需担忧	I never have to.
Dialogue: 0,02:19:37.28,02:19:38.28,Default,,0,0,0,,你没事吧	You okay?
Dialogue: 0,02:19:39.28,02:19:41.28,Default,,0,0,0,,你从未像现在这么帅	You've never looked better.
Dialogue: 0,02:19:41.28,02:19:43.28,Default,,0,0,0,,别这样 拜托	Don't. Please.
Dialogue: 0,02:19:44.28,02:19:46.28,Default,,0,0,0,,我们有多险	How close were we?
Dialogue: 0,02:19:49.28,02:19:50.28,Default,,0,0,0,,跟往常一样	The usual.
Dialogue: 0,02:19:54.28,02:19:55.28,Default,,0,0,0,,跟往常一样	The usual?
Dialogue: 0,02:19:57.28,02:19:59.28,Default,,0,0,0,,请别逗我笑	Please don't make me laugh.
